{
  "stem": "942.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she came running into the house when the gendarmes came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was telling my mother-- she says, Ethel, what are you doing with this baby.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where are you taking this child, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Leave the child with me, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was begging, you know, to leave this baby with her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, my mother would not leave the baby, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that time, my father-- I remember this-- that he was trying to hand her something in a little cotton bag, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the gendarmes caught him, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They caught his hand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took away this bag that was-- and I remember, the gendarme sort of poured it out on his hand.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember these gold-- gold coins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were called Maria Theresas, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were gold ducats, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were some-- and some rings, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wanted to leave it with her, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so it was absolutely chaos, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were marched out from the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we left everything behind, you know, our furniture, linen, and, you know, everything, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very upset about the dogs, that I have to leave my dogs, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as we were taken out of the house, all these neighbors were standing around, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody really had anything good to say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in fact, I found out that, after we went around the corner, you know, all these neighbors, they descended on our home, like in every other Jewish home where the people were taken out.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they looted everything that could be moved, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, eventually, they moved in.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
